OL,3,CShould the Channel Islands give carers
OL,4,Cunpaid leave?
OL,6,F"There are times when you need a day
OL,7,Foff because my mum is not well, or she
OL,8,Fhas appointments and so we need time
OL,9,Foff for that.
OL,11,F"When I leave work, it's almost like
OL,12,Fmy second shift until bedtime.
OL,14,F"Without that, we've got no care.
OL,15,FWithout that, there's a waiting list
OL,16,Fand we wouldn't be able to work.
