OL,3,CShould the Channel Islands give carers
OL,4,Cunpaid leave?
OL,6,F"My mother can't live on her own, so
OL,7,Fpotentially she could be in a home.
OL,8,FAnd I know she doesn't want that, so
OL,9,Fwe're able to make it work like this,
OL,10,Ffor now."
OL,12,FThe UK scheme came into effect on
OL,13,FSaturday 6 April 2024, helping carers
OL,14,Fmanage their responsibilities outside
OL,15,Fof work, such as caring for someone
OL,16,Fwho has a disability, needs elderly
OL,17,Fcare or has a long-term illness
OL,18,Flasting more than three months.
