OL,3,CShould the Channel Islands give carers
OL,4,Cunpaid leave?
OL,6,FPeter Harwood, Chair of Carers
OL,7,FGuernsey says voluntary carers are
OL,8,Fvital in saving the island money:
OL,9,F"Close to #30 million would be the
OL,10,Fcost to the States of Guernsey if it
OL,11,Fhad to provide all of the care and
OL,12,Fthat's why I'd like to see them lead
OL,13,Fby example and not wait for statute,
OL,14,Fjust go ahead an introduce this
OL,15,Fbenefit."
OL,17,FPoliticians across the Channel Islands
OL,18,Fhave differing views on how to move
OL,19,Fforward.
